II: \; \sqrt{xy}=15 \Leftrightarrow\sqrt x=\frac{15}{\sqrt y}
I
\frac{15}{\sqrt y}+\sqrt y=8 \Leftrightarrow15+y=8 \sqrt y \Leftrightarrow y-8 \sqrt y+15=0
